name: Wheel Boys Bicycle
details: The Cybot bike comes equipped with a single-speed freewheel transmission. Designed for the young rider taking their first rides with removable stabilizers and height-adjustable saddle and handlebars. A stylish red frame and rims are the background for a matching full chainguard and stabilizers.

name: Portable Loo - Unisex
details: Fast help when you're in need! If you can't get to the toilet in time, then the UNISEX urine bottle comes discretely to your rescue. Whether you are on a long car journey with kids or need for an emergency, it will always be there for you if needs be.
